{"tid":409904,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"見到寵物店同住家繁殖啲貓就覺得好慘","createTime":"2017-09-22T12:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T22:58:31.000Z","uid":35411,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"053b2afd2b23ae19899f2891edd7603c26967663","tid":409904,"uid":35411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"幾日前經過寵物店見到幾隻布偶貓好活潑好得意。<br />\n<br />\n有隻個紋好似有隻蝴蝶係對眼到咁，就覺得好治癒好想帶佢返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n返屋企上網研究下喇，就揾到個自家繁殖岀讓嘅比寵物店平好多，咁就whatsapp 佢睇下喇<br />\n<br />\n一睇就岀事喇<br />\n<br />\n啲貓b好似奴隸咁瑟縮係個盒到好似好驚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貓媽個樣又好似好可憐咁<br />\n<br />\n睇到我好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都知我唔應該揾呢啲貓販子，所以我都無理佢<br />\n<br />\n頭先佢腥左張圖黎，係一隻15個月大嘅貓女，未絕育，雖然真係好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟應該救佢脱苦海定扺制貓販子？但後者隻貓就可能淪為生仔機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f27fc57fac4de644145710ddcf0ce1f29c4f959","tid":409904,"uid":35411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"<em>testing</em>"},{"pid":"47dfdc7e803ac26c87774e2e8cce8942e996ba8d","tid":409904,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"我地保護唔到所有野 保護眼前嘅嘢 做個偽善嘅人就夠"},{"pid":"2e89d62e93d714e8d66d3bf61f677ab264dfa200","tid":409904,"uid":35411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39ba468a92db2421d8f0349a4d527bff62cff84","tid":409904,"uid":149150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/409900/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/409900/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n麻煩請廣傳"},{"pid":"d8e680c91731b2fe3a9b418d48bdfeafcf01d012","tid":409904,"uid":7752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T22:58:31.000Z","msg":"想問下邊間自家繁殖既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}